Karnataka: Collision between lorry and tempo kills 13 
18-3-2017 
13 persons were killed in a collision between lorry and tempo in Chitradurga, Karnataka. (Source: ANI) 13 persons were killed in a collision between lorry and tempo in Chitradurga, Karnataka. (Source: ANI)

A total of 13 persons were killed in a collision between lorry and tempo in Chitradurga, Karnataka. The lorry driver is reported to be absconding after the incident.

